com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.maps

Interface OnMapReadyCallback


  • public interface OnMapReadyCallback
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked when the map is ready to be used.

    Once an instance of this interface is set on a MapFragment or MapView object, the onMapReady(MapboxMap) method is triggered when the map is ready to be used and provides a non-null instance of MapboxMap.
